entry.title: gbirke/docx2dokuwiki-xsl
entry.summary:
Stylesheet to convert DOCX files to dokuwiki text

This project is for creating an XSLT stylesheet converting DOCX files (and their contents) to DokuWiki markup.

https://www.dokuwiki.org/wiki:syntax
